NEGOTIATION

Linked Attribute: ^gCharisma^n

Negotiation is used to negotiate prices with shop keepers, paydata rates
and nuyen rewards from autoruns. It is a very handy skill to have, as it's
affects can sometimes be very large. Most negotiation tests revolve around
your Intelligence score also. Poor results in a negotiation test can result
in it working against your favour. Negotiation tests happen automatically.
